<div id="about-banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(27, 29, 29, 0.68) 0%, rgba(40, 53, 62, 0.6) 50%), url(<%= image_url 'guitar.jpg' %>);">
  <div class="banner-flex container">
    <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-12">
      <div class="about-banner-message">
        <h1>Welcome to Guitwise</h1>
        <h4>A community of guitarists learning from each other</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="about-second-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="about-card" style= "border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 1px; border-color: $gray;">
          <div class="about-card-header">
            <h4>Post</h4>
            <i class="fa fa-video-camera" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="about-card-content">
            <p>Post videos with questions about the music you are learning</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="about-card" style= "border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 1px; border-color: $gray;">
          <div class="about-card-header">
            <h4>Respond</h4>
            <i class="fa fa-comments" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="about-card-content">
            <p>Respond with videos to give feedback or show your progress</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="about-card">
          <div class="about-card-header">
            <h4>Share</h4>
            <i class="fa fa-bullhorn" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="about-card-content">
            <p>Share your knowledge with a short tutorial</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="about-page-wrapper">
  <div class="about-cards-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-lg-10">
          <div class="about-header">
            <h2>What is Guitwise?</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="about-card">
            <div class="about-card-icon">
              <i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="about-card-content">
              <p><strong>Guitwise has the mission to gather a community of musicians learning from each other. </strong></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-2">
          <div class="about-card">
            <div class="about-card-icon">
              <i class="fa fa-video-camera" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="about-card-content">
              <p>Sign up and post a short video with a question, showing exactly what you want to learn or where you are stuck in your music. <strong>Musicians from around the world will come to help you out by posting short video tutorials to share their knowledge and expertise!</strong></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="about-card">
            <div class="about-card-icon">
              <i class="fa fa-bullhorn" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="about-card-content">
              <p>You can also vote on questions you found pertinent, responses you thought that helped you out the best or down vote the ones you found not helpful at all.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Start now</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
